\chapter{Literature Review}
\label{cha:literature_review}

This chapter provides the overview of hand tracking research. Review on early hand tracking research has been published on \cite{pavlovic1997}, \cite{wu1999} and \cite{erol2007}. Next section describes the different types of hand tracking techniques. Section \ref{cha2:sec:human_body_tracking} discuss the similarities and differences between whole human body and the hand tracking techniques. In Section \ref{cha2:sec:rationale_of_selected_techniques} rationale behind selected methodologies/techniques for this thesis have been discussed. Remaining sections describes features, sampling techniques, probabilistic graphical model and hand joints detection techniques related with this thesis.


